         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>EFU-10012 Bergen Town Hall — Consulting Engineer for concrete rehabilitation at Bergen Town Hall.</P>
            </TITLE>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="71310000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Bergen kommune, the Agency for Development, hereby invites tenderers to a competition for a contract for consulting engineer for the engineering design and technical control for rehabilitation of concrete façades at Bergen Town Hall.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <n2016:NUTS CODE="NO051"/>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>Bergen Town Hall is drawn by architect Ealing Viking, and was built in the period 1971-74.</P>
                  <P>The construction consists of 14 floors and contains primarily offices, meeting rooms, canteen and technical rooms distributed throughout the canteen wing and tower block. The main construction is slabs, walls and columns made of in situ concrete. The Town Hall has a total GFA of 11,277 m<FT TYPE="SUP">2</FT>.</P>
                  <P>The façades at Bergen Town Hall have wide range corrosive damages. In 2016, the Town Council allocated funds for improvement of these the Town Council undertook on 5.17, that also engineering design of internal rehabilitation shall be implemented.</P>
                  <P>It is desirable that the facade rehabilitation and internal reconstruction are carried out simultaneously.</P>
                  <P>The Town Hall will be vacant at the time of the works. The current plan indicates that the building must be empty and clear of internal demolition works by the end of 2018/19.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <AC_QUALITY>
                  <AC_CRITERION>Personnel competence</AC_CRITERION>
                  <AC_WEIGHTING>40-50 %</AC_WEIGHTING>
               </AC_QUALITY>
               <AC_QUALITY>
                  <AC_CRITERION>Assignment comprehension</AC_CRITERION>
                  <AC_WEIGHTING>20-30 %</AC_WEIGHTING>
               </AC_QUALITY>
               <AC_PRICE>
                  <AC_WEIGHTING>20-30 %</AC_WEIGHTING>
               </AC_PRICE>
               <DURATION TYPE="MONTH">30</DURATION>
               <NO_RENEWAL/>
               <NO_ACCEPTED_VARIANTS/>
               <NO_OPTIONS/>
               <NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
         </OBJECT_CONTRACT>
